0x82BA3F88// GetInteriorRoomTimecycle
int GET_INTERIOR_ROOM_TIMECYCLE(int interiorId, int roomIndex);Parameters:interiorId: The target interior.roomIndex: Interior room index.Returns: Room's timecycle hash.Examples:Lualocal playerPed = PlayerPedId()
local interiorId = GetInteriorFromEntity(playerPed)
local roomHash = GetRoomKeyFromEntity(playerPed)
local roomId = GetInteriorRoomIndexByHash(interiorId, roomHash)

if roomId ~= -1 then
  local roomTimecycle = GetInteriorRoomTimecycle(interiorId, roomId)
  print("current room timecycle hash is: " .. roomTimecycle)
end

// GetInteriorRoomTimecycle
int GET_INTERIOR_ROOM_TIMECYCLE(int interiorId, int roomIndex);

local playerPed = PlayerPedId()
local interiorId = GetInteriorFromEntity(playerPed)
local roomHash = GetRoomKeyFromEntity(playerPed)
local roomId = GetInteriorRoomIndexByHash(interiorId, roomHash)

if roomId ~= -1 then
  local roomTimecycle = GetInteriorRoomTimecycle(interiorId, roomId)
  print("current room timecycle hash is: " .. roomTimecycle)
end
